@startuml
title XML Display & Editing Application\nLayered Architecture — Component View

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam ArrowColor #444444
skinparam NoteBorderColor #888888
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7

skinparam package {
  BorderColor #444444
  FontStyle bold
  FontSize 12
}

skinparam component {
  BorderColor #444444
  BackgroundColor white
  FontSize 10
}

'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
' LAYER 4 — PRESENTATION
'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
package "Layer 4: Presentation" #D6EAF8 {
  [XMLApplication] as App
  [XMLDisplay]     as Display
}

note top of App
  **Constraint:** Only layer that reads stdin / writes stdout.
  Translates user intent into Layer 3 calls.
  Never mutates the Domain directly.
end note

'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
' LAYER 3 — APPLICATION LOGIC
'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
package "Layer 3: Application Logic" #D5F5E3 {
  [XMLLoader]    as Loader
  [XMLEditor]    as Editor
  [XMLValidator] as Validator
}

note right of Validator
  **Constraint:** Schema rules determine
  which elements/attributes are valid.
  Empty schema → all operations permitted.
end note

note right of Loader
  **Relaxed layering:** XMLLoader calls
  both Layer 1 (XMLTokenizer) and
  Layer 2 (dom::Document factory).
  Exception: directly instantiates
  Document_Impl to create the root document.
end note

'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
' LAYER 2 — DOMAIN
'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
package "Layer 2: Domain" #FEF9E7 {
  package "Interfaces (dom:: namespace)" #FDEBD0 {
    [dom::Document] as IDoc
    [dom::Element]  as IElem
    [dom::Node]     as INode
    [dom::Attr]     as IAttr
    [dom::Text]     as IText
  }
  package "Implementations (*_Impl)" #FDFEFE {
    [Document_Impl] as DImpl
    [Element_Impl]  as EImpl
    [Node_Impl]     as NImpl
    [Attr_Impl]     as AImpl
    [Text_Impl]     as TImpl
  }
}

note bottom of INode
  **Constraint:** Upper layers interact with
  the Domain through dom:: interfaces.
  The interface package is the stable Facade
  exposed to Layers 3 and 4.
  Composite pattern: every Node can hold
  child Nodes, forming the XML tree.
end note

'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
' LAYER 1 — INFRASTRUCTURE
'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
package "Layer 1: Infrastructure" #FDEDEC {
  [XMLTokenizer]  as Tokenizer
  [XMLSerializer] as Serializer
}

note bottom of Tokenizer
  **Constraint:** No dependency on any
  layer above. Knows only XML syntax,
  not the DOM data model.
end note

'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
' RELATIONSHIPS
'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

' Layer 4 internal peer call
App     --> Display    : renders / resolves node index

' Layer 4 → Layer 3
App     --> Loader     : load(filename) : Document*
App     --> Editor     : addElement / setAttribute\nremoveElement / addText / save

' Layer 4 → Layer 2 (read-only: Display casts each node to its concrete interface)
Display ..> INode      : getNodeType / getChildNodes\n<<read-only>>
Display ..> IElem      : getTagName / getAttributes\n<<read-only>>
Display ..> IAttr      : getName / getValue\n<<read-only>>
Display ..> IText      : getData\n<<read-only>>

' Layer 3 internal
Editor  --> Validator  : canAddElement\ncanAddAttribute / canAddText

' Layer 3 → Layer 2
Loader  --> DImpl      : <<creates>> new Document_Impl()
Loader  --> IDoc       : createElement / createTextNode\nappendChild (root)
Loader  --> IElem      : setAttribute / appendChild
Editor  --> IDoc       : createElement / createTextNode
Editor  --> IElem      : setAttribute / removeAttribute\nhasAttribute / appendChild
Editor  --> INode      : getParentNode / removeChild

' Layer 3 → Layer 1  (relaxed: skips Layer 2 for I/O)
Loader  --> Tokenizer  : getNextToken()
Editor  --> Serializer : serializePretty()

' Layer 2: *_Impl classes implement dom:: interfaces
IDoc    <|.. DImpl     : implements
IElem   <|.. EImpl     : implements
INode   <|.. NImpl     : implements
IAttr   <|.. AImpl     : implements
IText   <|.. TImpl     : implements

' Layer 2: Composite — all node types extend dom::Node
IDoc  --|> INode
IElem --|> INode
IAttr --|> INode
IText --|> INode

@enduml
